#: addons/Planetae_Numero_Duos_Mk_2_1.wad/addon:4 input:8 input:9 input:10
#: standard
msgid "Planetae Numero Duos Mk 2.1"
msgstr ""

#: addons/Planetae_Numero_Duos_Mk_2_1.wad/addon:5 input:6 input:10 standard
msgid ""
"Important !! This Map depends on foreign_planet.wad by Nordfriese.   This is "
"the Second Planet to be inhabited by Humans.      There have been previous "
"attempts at colonizing these land areas.  There are adequate minerals, "
"flora , fauna and aquatic life on the two main land masses. However, there "
"is a complete lack of Gold on these areas.     Previous pioneers have "
"transported a small quantity of Gold from the Volcanic islands and buried it "
"in small mines close to the water's edge. They have market these mines with "
"Standing Stones.  The pioneers also used Standing Stones to mark some of the "
"good fishing areas."
msgstr ""
"Important!! Aquest mapa depèn de foreign_planet.wad de Nordfriese.   Aquest "
"és el segon planeta habitat per humans.      Hi ha hagut intents anteriors "
"de colonitzar aquestes zones terrestres.  Hi ha minerals, flora, fauna i "
"vida aquàtica adequats a les dues masses terrestres principals. Tanmateix, "
"hi ha una manca total d'or en aquestes àrees.     Els pioners anteriors han "
"transportat una petita quantitat d'or de les illes volcàniques i l'han "
"enterrat en petites mines prop de la vora de l'aigua. Han comercialitzat "
"aquestes mines amb Standing Stones.  Els pioners també van utilitzar "
"Standing Stones per marcar algunes de les bones zones de pesca."

#: addons/Planetae_Numero_Duos_Mk_2_1.wad/dirnames:4 standard input:4
msgid "Add-On Maps"
msgstr "Mapes del complement"

#: input:7 input:11 standard
msgid ""
"Due to the Gold restrictions on the Main Lands, it is recomended that you do "
"not begin to build your Army before you establish a Gold mine on a Volcanic "
"Island.  Locate your local man made Gold mine and build the Port that is "
"close by. There is enough Gold in this mine to build several ports. Build a "
"couple of ships and explore the Volcanic islands.  Secondly, in order to "
"access the islands in the second large body of water, you need to build a "
"port on that side of your domain and build a second fleet of ships."
msgstr ""
"A causa de les restriccions d'or a les terres principals, es recomana que no "
"comenceu a construir el vostre exèrcit abans d'establir una mina d'or a una "
"illa volcànica.  Localitzeu la vostra mina d'or feta per l'home local i "
"construïu el port que hi ha a prop. Hi ha prou or en aquesta mina per "
"construir diversos ports. Construeix un parell de vaixells i explora les "
"illes volcàniques.  En segon lloc, per accedir a les illes de la segona gran "
"massa d'aigua, heu de construir un port en aquest costat del vostre domini i "
"construir una segona flota de vaixells."
